OL,3,CTwo charged with murder after teens
OL,4,Ckilled in crash
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter two people died in a crash
OL,8,Finvolving a BMW and a motorbike.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FAberthaw Road in Newport in the early
OL,12,Fhours of Thursday, where two people
OL,13,Fwere pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,15,FGwent Police named the victims as 19-
OL,16,Fyear-old Jaydon Bowyer and 16-year-old
OL,17,FTashay Canoville, the driver and
OL,18,Fpillion passenger of the motorbike.
