OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778573162
OL,3,CTwo charged with murder after teens
OL,4,Ckilled in crash
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old from Newport and a 34-
OL,7,Fyear-old man were arrested on Thursday
OL,8,Fand later charged with murder, police
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe men have been remanded into police
OL,12,Fcustody and are due to appear before
OL,13,FNewport Magistrates' Court on Monday.
OL,15,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,16,FDetective Superintendent Steven
OL,17,FMaloney, said: "Both Jaydon and
OL,18,FTashay's families are being supported
OL,19,Fby specialist officers and our
OL,20,Fthoughts remain with them at this
OL,21,Fdifficult time.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
