OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778573162
OL,3,CTwo charged with murder after teens
OL,4,Ckilled in crash
OL,6,F"We would like to thank the community
OL,7,Ffor their support while we continue to
OL,8,Finvestigate fully the circumstances of
OL,9,Fthese tragic deaths."
OL,11,FHe added: "We understand that reports
OL,12,Fof this nature can be concerning to
OL,13,Four communities.
OL,15,F"We have been working around the clock
OL,16,Fto gather and assess evidence and we
OL,17,Fhave liaised closely with our
OL,18,Fcolleagues in the CPS to reach these
OL,19,Ftwo charging decisions.
