OL,3,CTwo charged with murder after teens
OL,4,Ckilled in crash
OL,6,F"While our enquiries continue over the
OL,7,Fcoming days, you are likely to see an
OL,8,Fincreased number of officers in the
OL,9,Farea."
OL,11,FPolice confirmed two women aged 24 and
OL,12,F40 from Newport who had earlier been
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of murder have
OL,14,Fbeen released.
